# 1. READ ASSET
read_verilog rtl/*.v

# 2. HIERARCHY & PRE-OPTIMIZE
hierarchy -check -top system
proc; opt; fsm; opt; memory; opt

# 3. XILINX MAPPING (Zynq-7000 Target)
# This handles the LUT6, CARRY4, and DSP48E1 mapping
synth_xilinx -top system

# 4. AREA REPORT (The "A" in PPA)
# Shows exactly where your 2283 LCs are
stat -width

# 5. TIMING ANALYSIS (The "P" in PPA)